OL,7,Fchild who was well liked by all.
OL,9,F"This is reflected in the funeral
OL,10,Fservice the school has arranged for
OL,11,FShay, and shares with all who knew
OL,12,Fher, what a special girl she was,
OL,13,Fthrough words, pictures and music.
OL,15,F"School is at the heart of the
OL,16,Fcommunity, and we know this day will
OL,17,Fhelp everyone who knew her to share
OL,18,Ftheir respects and pay tribute to the
OL,19,Fbright, fun-loving girl, and continue
OL,20,Fus on the road to healing after this
OL,21,Fdevastating event.
